# Engine-native decagonal star-and-cross field (Tenet 26 — use the girih primitive,
# don't hand-author tiles). girih field grows a GAP-FREE decagonal tiling; each
# tile carries its hankin-star decoration. Gap-free = shared edges = the no-gap
# precondition PIC needs to JOIN per-tile outlines into the continuous lattice.
blueprint g
  circle C0 center(0,0) radius 100

pattern p on g
  girih field decagonal 30 shells 1
